short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds numbers to Google search results for quick navigation

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
For those who have always wanted "WASD" controls for the internet, this extension adds keyboard shortcuts to the Chrome search page. 

Features:
- Results are labeled with a number, for example pressing "1" navigates to the first link
- Navigate to the images tab by hitting "i" and back to the All tab by hitting "a"

If you have feature requests, feel free to reach out to @oldestasian on Twitter!

Version history:
1.0.3 9/26/24: fix search results not enumerating, should be good for a while now. 
1.0.2 9/23/24: fix images/all tab not working due to new google search HTML format. Now it searches by text so unfortunately this is English only for now. 
1.0.1 9/1/24: update xpath to fix functionality for new google search format. 
1.0: release
